test_presence_of_duplicates_in_result:
assert (2 == 3)
 +  where 2 = <built-in method count of list object at 0x75290b4a6300>([-779])
 +    where <built-in method count of list object at 0x75290b4a6300> = [[1, -779], [1, -779, 1], [-779, 1], [-779, 1, -779], [1, -779], [1, -779, 1], ...].count
test_if_sublist_product_equals_number:
assert -606841 == -779
 +  where -606841 = <built-in function prod>([-19, -41, -779])
 +    where <built-in function prod> = math.prod
